# demo.tape — ClaudeGlance CLI demo (reproducibility tape)
# The committed demo.gif was captured via Kap (menu-bar GUI recording, not VHS-native).
# This tape reproduces the CLI-launch portion. For full GUI demo, use Kap.
# Regenerate CLI-only: vhs demo.tape
Output demo-cli.gif

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set Theme "Dracula"

Type "claude-glance --version"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "claude-glance"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 2s
